《'''黌宮雙燕'''》（[[英語|英語]]：{{lang|en|''Our Hearts Were Growing Up''}}）是一齣[[1946年電影|1946年]]的[[美國電影|美國]][[喜劇電影|喜劇電影]]，由{{tsl|en|William D. Russell (director)|威廉·D·羅素}}導演，{{tsl|en|Melvin Frank|麥雲·法蘭克}}、{{tsl|en|Norman Panama|諾曼·派拉馬}}和{{tsl|en|Frank Waldman|法蘭克·華德曼}}編劇，此片是1944年電影《{{tsl|en|Our Hearts Were Young and Gay (film)|有女懷春}}》的續集。影片主演有{{tsl|en|Gail Russell|姬·羅素}}、{{tsl|en|Diana Lynn|丹娜·蓮}}、{{tsl|en|Brian Donlevy|柏賴恩·當尼威}}、{{tsl|en|Billy De Wolfe|比利·迪·胡央}}、{{tsl|en|James Brown (actor)|詹姆士·布朗 (演員)|詹姆士·布朗}}以及{{tsl|en|Bill Edwards (actor)|比爾·愛德華茲 (演員)|比爾·愛德華茲}}等，由[[派拉蒙電影|派拉蒙電影]]上映於1946年6月16日。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/85926/Our-Hearts-Were-Growing-Up/ |title=Our Hearts Were Growing Up (1946) - Overview |publisher=TCM.com |date= |accessdate=2015-06-30 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924160038/http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/title/85926/Our-Hearts-Were-Growing-Up/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/120059/Our-Hearts-Were-Growing-Up/overview |title=Our-Hearts-Were-Growing-Up - Trailer - Cast - Showtimes |publisher=NYTimes.com |date= |accessdate=2015-06-30 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307102802/http://www.nytimes.com/movies/movie/120059/Our-Hearts-Were-Growing-Up/overview |dead-url=no }}</ref>

